&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "3",
&"next_id": "4",
&"text": "Don't \"yes honey\" me!! 😭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"30": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "30",
&"next_id": "31",
&"text": "My my, I've been getting a little nostalgic seeing all your pictures",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"31": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "31",
&"next_id": "32",
&"text": "It reminded me of my college days",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"32": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "32",
&"next_id": "33",
&"text": "You never talked about it much 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"33": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "33",
&"next_id": "34",
&"text": "You met dad there right?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"34": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "34",
&"next_id": "35",
&"text": "I did 🙈",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"35": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "35",
&"next_id": "36",
&"text": "How come you never talked about it? 🤔",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"36": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "36",
&"next_id": "37",
&"text": "Well it's a long and complicated story but maybe now you're old enough to hear some of the girl talk 🤭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"37": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "37",
&"next_id": "38",
&"text": "Mom used to be hip and cool y'know 😌",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"38": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "38",
&"next_id": "39",
&"text": "Mom, NOBODY says \"hip and cool\" 😂",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"39": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "39",
&"next_id": "40",
&"text": "Really? Well anyway!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"4": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "4",
&"next_id": "5",
&"text": "That guy on my post?? You literally told him he could take me out on a date!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"40": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "40",
&"next_id": "41",
&"text": "Do you want to hear about my very first college date?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"41": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "41",
&"next_id": "42",
&"text": "Omg yess!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"42": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "42",
&"next_id": "43",
&"text": "I was so nervous, I changed outfits like five times",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"43": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "43",
&"next_id": "44",
&"text": "Same 😆",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"44": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "44",
&"next_id": "45",
&"text": "I wore this little sundress that I thought made me look so grown up",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"45": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "45",
&"next_id": "46",
&"text": "I like to keep all my pictures on my phone",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"46": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "46",
&"next_id": "47",
&"text": "Let me see..",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"47": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "47",
&"next_id": "48",
&"text": "Oh here it is!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"48": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "48",
&"next_id": "49",
&"text": "img: mom/2",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"49": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "49",
&"next_id": "50",
&"text": "I don't remember you taking this picture of me? 🤔",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"5": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "5",
&"next_id": "6",
&"text": "Why would you do that??",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"50": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "50",
&"next_id": "51",
&"text": "That's your momma 😂",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"51": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "51",
&"next_id": "52",
&"text": "Whaaa??",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"52": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "52",
&"next_id": "53",
&"text": "Is that seriously you??",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"53": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "53",
&"next_id": "54",
&"text": "Omg you look just like me!?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"54": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "54",
&"next_id": "55",
&"text": "Of course, how do you think babies work honey 😂",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"55": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "55",
&"next_id": "56",
&"text": "Omg that's so cute 😭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"56": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "56",
&"next_id": "57",
&"text": "I'm a mini version of mom 🥹🩷",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"57": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "57",
&"next_id": "58",
&"text": "Where did you go? What did you do?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"58": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "58",
&"next_id": "59",
&"text": "He took me to this tiny restaurant near our little campus",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"59": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "59",
&"next_id": "60",
&"text": "It was nothing fancy but I felt like a princess haha",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"6": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "6",
&"next_id": "7",
&"text": "What? No no honey",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"60": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "60",
&"next_id": "61",
&"text": "He was a really sweet boy, did everything to make me feel comfortable",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"61": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "61",
&"next_id": "62",
&"text": "I don't know how to explain it",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"62": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "62",
&"next_id": "63",
&"text": "Like your heart is beating so fast you can barely eat",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"63": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "63",
&"next_id": "64",
&"text": "img: mom/3",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"64": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "64",
&"next_id": "65",
&"text": "That's SO adorable mom 🥰",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"65": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "65",
&"next_id": "66",
&"text": "I remember I could barely look him in the eyes, I was that shy",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"66": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "66",
&"next_id": "67",
&"text": "And he was too! It was a whole cute experience 🥰",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"67": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "67",
&"next_id": "68",
&"text": "But when our eyes met, it was like we were the only two in the world hehe",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"68": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "68",
&"next_id": "69",
&"text": "I'd never felt anything like that before that point",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"69": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "69",
&"next_id": "70",
&"text": "Aww 🥺 Were you seriously in love?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"7": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "7",
&"next_id": "8",
&"text": "I thought he was a new friend! 🫢",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"70": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "70",
&"next_id": "71",
&"text": "Head over heels, he was my first and only at the time",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"71": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "71",
&"next_id": "72",
&"text": "We were neighbors too so we spent all day every day together!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"72": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "72",
&"next_id": "73",
&"text": "He was all I'd think about",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"73": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "73",
&"next_id": "74",
&"text": "So what happened if you and dad felt that strongly about each other 🫠",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"74": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "74",
&"next_id": "75",
&"text": "I didn't know you knew him for that long!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"75": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "75",
&"next_id": "76",
&"text": "What went wrong? 🥺",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"76": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "76",
&"next_id": "77",
&"text": "Oh",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"77": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "77",
&"next_id": "78",
&"text": "No honey, that wasn't your father 🤭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"78": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "78",
&"next_id": "79",
&"text": "That was a boy I grew up with",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"79": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "79",
&"next_id": "80",
&"text": "Wait what??",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"8": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "8",
&"next_id": "9",
&"text": "He said he wanted to take you out so I assumed he meant like a nice friendly outing",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"80": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "80",
&"next_id": "81",
&"text": "Mhmm! Your dad came after him 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"81": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "81",
&"next_id": "82",
&"text": "But that's a story for another time 😊",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"82": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "82",
&"next_id": "83",
&"text": "Wait seriously? 🥹 That was such a cute story but I feel really sad",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"83": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "83",
&"next_id": "84",
&"text": "Well if I kept seeing him, I wouldn't have had you 🥰",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"84": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "84",
&"next_id": "85",
&"text": "I guess, but that's still so sad 😣",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"85": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "85",
&"next_id": "86",
&"text": "I'll tell you the rest when I can honey, mom's got chores to do",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"86": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "86",
&"next_id": "87",
&"text": "And Ms Whiskers is meowing at me",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"87": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "87",
&"next_id": "88",
&"text": "Give her some extra treats 😍",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"88": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "88",
&"next_id": "89",
&"text": "I will! Love you baby ❤️",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"89": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "89",
&"next_id": "90",
&"text": "Love you Mom 😭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"9": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "9",
&"next_id": "10",
&"text": "Mom he was clearly saying weird stuff 😭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
