raw_text = "~ start
PlayerM: Mom!
Mom: Yes honey? 😊
PlayerM: Don't \"yes honey\" me!! 😭
PlayerM: That guy on my post?? You literally told him he could take me out on a date!
PlayerM: Why would you do that??
Mom: What? No no honey
Mom: I thought he was a new friend! 🫢
Mom: He said he wanted to take you out so I assumed he meant like a nice friendly outing
PlayerM: Mom he was clearly saying weird stuff 😭
Mom: Sorry darling, I had no idea!
Mom: I won't respond to your friends again! 😇
PlayerM: Ugh he's NOT my friend 🙄
Mom: 🫢
Mom: You know I'm not good with all this social media stuff
Mom: I just wanted to be supportive of you honey
PlayerM: ...
PlayerM: Okay fine, I know you were just trying to be nice
PlayerM: But please don't do that again 😩
Mom: I promise promise I'll be more careful sweetheart 🙈
Mom: But you know
Mom: Seeing your date photo really made me smile
Mom: You looked so beautiful
Mom: Seriously making Mom feel old haha
Mom: img: mom/1
PlayerM: Thanks mom 🥺 You're not old though
Mom: Oh Mabel, you don't know how fast time flies honey 😊
Mom: But I'm happy because you're the best daughter I could ask for
PlayerM: I love you mom 🥺🩷
Mom: Love you too precious 😘
Mom: My my, I've been getting a little nostalgic seeing all your pictures
Mom: It reminded me of my college days
PlayerM: You never talked about it much 😅
PlayerM: You met dad there right?
Mom: I did 🙈
PlayerM: How come you never talked about it? 🤔
Mom: Well it's a long and complicated story but maybe now you're old enough to hear some of the girl talk 🤭
Mom: Mom used to be hip and cool y'know 😌
PlayerM: Mom, NOBODY says \"hip and cool\" 😂
Mom: Really? Well anyway!
Mom: Do you want to hear about my very first college date?
PlayerM: Omg yess!
Mom: I was so nervous, I changed outfits like five times
PlayerM: Same 😆
Mom: I wore this little sundress that I thought made me look so grown up
Mom: I like to keep all my pictures on my phone
Mom: Let me see..
Mom: Oh here it is!
Mom: img: mom/2
PlayerM: I don't remember you taking this picture of me? 🤔
Mom: That's your momma 😂
PlayerM: Whaaa??
PlayerM: Is that seriously you??
PlayerM: Omg you look just like me!?
Mom: Of course, how do you think babies work honey 😂
PlayerM: Omg that's so cute 😭 
PlayerM: I'm a mini version of mom 🥹🩷
PlayerM: Where did you go? What did you do?
Mom: He took me to this tiny restaurant near our little campus
Mom: It was nothing fancy but I felt like a princess haha
Mom: He was a really sweet boy, did everything to make me feel comfortable
Mom: I don't know how to explain it
Mom: Like your heart is beating so fast you can barely eat
Mom: img: mom/3
PlayerM: That's SO adorable mom 🥰
Mom: I remember I could barely look him in the eyes, I was that shy
Mom: And he was too! It was a whole cute experience 🥰
Mom: But when our eyes met, it was like we were the only two in the world hehe
Mom: I'd never felt anything like that before that point
PlayerM: Aww 🥺 Were you seriously in love?
Mom: Head over heels, he was my first and only at the time
Mom: We were neighbors too so we spent all day every day together! 
Mom: He was all I'd think about
PlayerM: So what happened if you and dad felt that strongly about each other 🫠 
PlayerM: I didn't know you knew him for that long!
PlayerM: What went wrong? 🥺
Mom: Oh
Mom: No honey, that wasn't your father 🤭 
Mom: That was a boy I grew up with
PlayerM: Wait what??
Mom: Mhmm! Your dad came after him 😅
Mom: But that's a story for another time 😊
PlayerM: Wait seriously? 🥹 That was such a cute story but I feel really sad
Mom: Well if I kept seeing him, I wouldn't have had you 🥰
PlayerM: I guess, but that's still so sad 😣
Mom: I'll tell you the rest when I can honey, mom's got chores to do
Mom: And Ms Whiskers is meowing at me
PlayerM: Give her some extra treats 😍
Mom: I will! Love you baby ❤️
PlayerM: Love you Mom 😭
=> END
"
